# Word Page Numbering (Roman + Arabic) – Quick Fix

## Section Setup
1. Insert **Section Break – Next Page** after cover page  
2. Insert another **Section Break – Next Page** before Chapter One  

## Disable Linking
For each new section:
- Double-click footer
- Go to Header & Footer Tools → Design
- Turn off **Link to Previous**

## Numbering
### Section 1 — Cover
- Design → Different First Page → No page number

### Section 2 — Preliminary pages
- Page Number → Format
- Style: **i, ii, iii…**
- Start at: **i**

### Section 3 — Main body
- Page Number → Format
- Style: **1, 2, 3**
- Start at: **1**

This achieves:
- Cover → none  
- TOC & prelims → i, ii, iii  
- Chapters → 1, 2, 3  
